 Nolan Miller featured at American Cancer Society show: Fashions and costumes 
by Nolan Miller -- who has designed for stars such as Elizabeth Taylor, Lana 
Turner, Sally Field and Sophia Loren -- will be featured at the South Coast 
Cancer League's annual show on Feb. 9 at the Irvine Marriott.  
