 * The gun lobby loves to use the phrase "law-abiding citizens" to refer to 
themselves, alleging that they, not the criminals, will be the ones harmed if 
guns are controlled. 
</P>
<P>
 But most murders are committed by people who are law-abiding citizens until 
they pull the trigger. 
