 Lilly to Divest Nine Subsidiaries: Eli Lilly & Co. said it will divest its 
medical devices and diagnostics operations to focus on its core pharmaceuticals 
business. Seven of the nine units are located in California.The final form of 
the divestiture has not been resolved, but the Indianapolis-based firm 
envisions forming a holding company for six of its medical device and 
