<P>
 "Carving Through Concrete: An Evening of New Dance Works," a series of solo 
dance works choreographed by seven graduate students from the CalArts School of 
Dance, will be performed Feb. 1 at 7 p.m. at the L.A. Central Public Library's 
Mark Taper Auditorium. 
</P>
