<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARTHQUAKE: THE LONG ROAD BACK; HOW TO GET HELP; A GUIDE TO COPING WITH THE 
QUAKE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Times researchers David Brady, Cecilia Rasmussen, Stephanie 
Stassel, Tracy Thomas and Nona Yates. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
