<P>
 One of two men wounded in a shootout that left gang peacemaker Tony Thomas 
dead last week has been charged as a suspect in the killing, police said 
Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Rodney Compton, 20, was arrested outside St. Francis Hospital on Saturday, the 
day after Thomas' death, and booked on suspicion of murder.Compton had returned 
