<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Diceon Electronics Inc.: The Irvine manufacturer of circuit boards and back 
panels reported a first-quarter net loss of $3.4 million, or 65 cents a share, 
compared to a year-earlier loss of $1.6 million, or 32 cents a share. Sales for 
the quarter ended Jan. 1 declined 16% to $24.3 million. 
</P>
