KABC 22.2 3. Home Improvement KABC 21.3 4. Beverly Hills, 90210 KTTV 18.7 5. 
Coach KABC 18.6 6. Murder, She Wrote KCBS 17.5 7. Seinfeld (9:30 p.m.) KNBC 
17.4 8. The Simpsons KTTV 17.3 9. Seinfeld KNBC 17.0 10. Melrose Place KTTV 
15.3 Weekly Averages ABC: 13.4 CBS: 13.3 NBC: 11.5 FOX: 7.3 Season to Date CBS: 
12.9 ABC: 12.7 NBC: 11.2 FOX: 7.1 DANIEL CERONE 
</P>
